{
  "id": "595f5ca5aff98e00118f9143",
  "title": "ラグランジュの平均値の定理",
  "created": 1499421878,
  "updated": 1499432870,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "595f5ca5aff98e00118f9143",
      "text": "ラグランジュの平均値の定理",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421878
    },
    {
      "id": "595f87a5aff09e0000e2687a",
      "text": "[$ \\frac{f(b) - f(a)}{b - a}=f'(c) ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499432870,
      "updated": 1499432870
    },
    {
      "id": "595f87a6aff09e0000e2687b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499432870,
      "updated": 1499432870
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb392",
      "text": "\t2つの実数[$ a < b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb395",
      "text": " 関数[$ f(x)] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb396",
      "text": "  閉区間[$ [a, b] ]  で連続",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb397",
      "text": "  開区間 [$ (a, b)] で微分可能",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb398",
      "text": " このとき開区間 [$ (a, b)] 上に、ある点 [$ c] が存在して以下が成り立つ:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb399",
      "text": " [$ \\frac{f(b) - f(a)}{b - a}=f'(c) ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39a",
      "text": " これを微分に関するラグランジュの平均値の定理という。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39b",
      "text": " 別表現として、ある [$ 0 < \\theta < 1]が存在して",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39c",
      "text": " [$ f(a + h) = f(a) + h f'(a + \\theta h)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39d",
      "text": "  以下の書き換えが行われているだけ[$ b = a + h, c = a + \\theta h]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421899
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5ccdaff09e00005cb3a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421901,
      "updated": 1499421901
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39e",
      "text": "ラグランジュの平均値の定理により [$ \\log(1 + x) = \\frac{x}{1 + \\theta x} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb39f",
      "text": "\tなぜなら",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb3a0",
      "text": " [$ a = 1, h = x] として",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb3a1",
      "text": " [$ \\log(1+x) = \\log(1) + x \\log'(1 + \\theta x)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb3a2",
      "text": " [$ \\log'(x) = 1/x, \\log(1) = 0]なので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb3a3",
      "text": " [$ \\log(1 + x) = \\frac{x}{1 + \\theta x} ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb3a4",
      "text": "\tlog(x)はx=0で微分できないので、xの絶対値は1より小さいことが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421885
    },
    {
      "id": "595f5cb5aff09e00005cb390",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1499421878,
      "updated": 1499421878
    }
  ]
}